{"title": "China\u2019s BYD is overtaking Tesla as the carmaker extraordinaire", "tags": "opinion", "timestamp": "2023-02-07", "content": "To get a sense of why Mr Akio Toyoda announced on Jan 26 that he would hand over the keys to the world\u2019s biggest carmaker to Mr Koji Sato, his No. 2, watch the surreal video from 2021 of the two of them driving Toyota\u2019s first Lexus electric vehicle (EV).\nMr Toyoda is at the wheel. At first, it is clear that he is a bit of an EV sceptic: He notes that the car feels heavy to drive. Then he puts his foot to the floor, and as the speed picks up, he whoops with joy like an overexcited Top Gun pilot."}